                    </div>

                    <br>
                    <br>
                    <a href="http://www.socioboard.com">
                        <img src="http://www.socioboard.com/Contents/img/ssp/logo-txt.png" alt=""></a>

                    <div style="width: 610px; height: auto; float: left; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; margin-top: 10px;">
                     @GlobusMultiLanguageLib.Resources.ForgotPasword_ForgotPassworMailBodydPartial_FollowFacebook <a href="https://www.facebook.com/SocioBoard">https://www.facebook.com/Socioboard</a>
